---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const lastUpdated = "January 11, 2026";
---

<Layout
	title="Terms & Services | tui.company"
	description="Terms and Services for tui.company."
>
	<main class="min-h-screen w-full bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(27,77,255,0.04)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(27,77,255,0.08)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:48px_48px]">
		<div class="w-[min(56rem,92vw)] mx-auto py-[clamp(3rem,7vw,5.5rem)] flex flex-col gap-[clamp(2rem,5vw,3.5rem)]">
			<a
				href="/"
				class="text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#6c7076] inline-flex items-center gap-2 transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-[#1b4dff]"
			>
				Back to home
			</a>
			<header class="flex flex-col gap-4">
				<p class="m-0 text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#6c7076]">
					Last updated {lastUpdated}
				</p>
				<h1 class="m-0 text-[clamp(2.8rem,8vw,5rem)] leading-[0.95] tracking-[-0.03em] uppercase">
					Terms <span class="text-[#1b4dff]">&amp; Services</span>
				</h1>
				<p class="m-0 max-w-[36rem] text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#6c7076]">
					These terms govern your access to tui.company and any related products
					or integrations.
				</p>
			</header>
			<div class="grid gap-8 border-t border-[rgba(27,77,255,0.2)] pt-8">
				<section class="grid gap-3">
					<h2 class="m-0 text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#6c7076]">
						Acceptance of terms
					</h2>
					<p class="m-0 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#6c7076]">
						By accessing or using tui.company and related services, you agree to
						these Terms and Services. If you do not agree, do not use the service.
					</p>
				</section>
				<section class="grid gap-3">
					<h2 class="m-0 text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#6c7076]">
						Service description
					</h2>
					<p class="m-0 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#6c7076]">
						tui.company provides terminal-first productivity tools and integrations,
						including scheduling and sync features. We may add, modify, or remove
						features over time.
					</p>
				</section>
				<section class="grid gap-3">
					<h2 class="m-0 text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#6c7076]">
						Acceptable use
					</h2>
					<ul class="m-0 pl-5 grid gap-2 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#6c7076] list-disc">
						<li>Do not use the service for unlawful, harmful, or abusive activity.</li>
						<li>
							Do not attempt to access data or systems you are not authorized to
							use.
						</li>
						<li>
							Do not interfere with or disrupt the service, including through
							excessive automated requests.
						</li>
					</ul>
				</section>
				<section class="grid gap-3">
					<h2 class="m-0 text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#6c7076]">
						Google services
					</h2>
					<p class="m-0 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#6c7076]">
						If you connect Google services, we request Google Calendar scopes to
						read and write calendar events and related metadata to provide syncing.
						You can revoke access at any time from your Google Account permissions
						page, which will disable calendar features.
					</p>
				</section>
				<section class="grid gap-3">
					<h2 class="m-0 text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#6c7076]">
						Intellectual property
					</h2>
					<p class="m-0 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#6c7076]">
						All software, branding, and content are owned by tui.company or its
						licensors. We grant you a limited, non-exclusive, revocable license to
						use the service as provided.
					</p>
				</section>
				<section class="grid gap-3">
					<h2 class="m-0 text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#6c7076]">
						Availability and changes
					</h2>
					<p class="m-0 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#6c7076]">
						The service is provided as available. We may change or discontinue the
						service or these terms. Continued use after updates means you accept
						the revised terms.
					</p>
				</section>
				<section class="grid gap-3">
					<h2 class="m-0 text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#6c7076]">
						Disclaimers
					</h2>
					<p class="m-0 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#6c7076]">
						The service is provided "as is" and "as available" without warranties
						of any kind. We do not warrant that the service will be uninterrupted,
						secure, or error free.
					</p>
				</section>
				<section class="grid gap-3">
					<h2 class="m-0 text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#6c7076]">
						Limitation of liability
					</h2>
					<p class="m-0 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#6c7076]">
						To the maximum extent permitted by law, tui.company will not be liable
						for indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages.
						Our total liability is limited to the amount you paid in the 12 months
						before the claim, or USD 100 if you paid nothing.
					</p>
				</section>
				<section class="grid gap-3">
					<h2 class="m-0 text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#6c7076]">
						Termination
					</h2>
					<p class="m-0 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#6c7076]">
						We may suspend or terminate access if you violate these terms or misuse
						the service. You may stop using the service at any time. Upon
						termination, your right to use the service ends.
					</p>
				</section>
				<section class="grid gap-3">
					<h2 class="m-0 text-[0.75rem] uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-[#6c7076]">
						Contact
					</h2>
					<p class="m-0 text-[0.95rem] leading-[1.8] text-[#6c7076]">
						Contact us at
						<a
							href="mailto:support@tui.company"
							class="text-[#1b4dff] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]"
						>
							tui.company@mariodev.xyz
						</a>
						.
					</p>
				</section>
			</div>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
